snippet.title: Boring Man - v2.0.0 Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The legendary stickman multiplayer game you've never heard of is back with a huge, brand new update!
The v2.0.0 beta is now available as free-to-play! Get in here!
🡆Download on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/346120/
🡆Download on GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/boring-man-online-tactical-stickman-combat/18422
🡆Join the discord: https://discord.gg/chtzQ4m
🡆Follow development on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpasmanGames
